       <div class="card events">
          <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/helping_elderly.jpg" alt="Helping the Elderly">
          <div class="card-body events">
            <h5 class="card-title events text-center">Helping the Elderly</h5>
            <p class="card-text events text-left">
            Spiritual Need!<br>
            <br>
            Recognize the end of life, rapidly declining health and crisis as a time for spiritual need, which may be defined differently by individuals but certainly needs to be part of everyone's care.<br>
            <br>
            "Our Mission is to Enrich the Quality of Life for Every Person We Meet", said Pastor Tony Freitas.<br>
            <br>
            We at A & Z God's Ministry for All People we have the privilege of leading a weekly worship service for residents of a local nursing home for several years. Through that worship service, we seek to reach out to all residents to share Christ's love.<br>
            <br>
            Places we Worship Regularly in: CareOne at Randolph / Southeast Rehabilitation North Easton / Copley At Stoughton / BayPointe Rehabilitation Center in Brockton. Call us for day and time. You are welcomed to attend all worship with us. We also do weekly visits to other nursing homes in our area.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

